      This site is an educational site and is safe for young viewers.

   If you have installed the latest version of the Flash Plugin (version
                    4.0), you may view the flash movie.

    If you do not have the latest version of the Flash Plugin (version
   4.0), you may choose to directly enter the SCO Kids' Site Home Page.

       To download the latest version of the flash plugin, visit the
                             Macromedia site.
